@model IEnumerable<BlogProj.Models.Post>
@using X.PagedList.Mvc.Core
@using X.PagedList.Web.Common
@using BlogProj.Services
@using X.PagedList
@inject IBlogFileService _fileService
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Index";
}

<h1 class="text-white">Posts</h1>
@if (User.IsInRole("Administrator"))
{
    <p class="text-white">
        <a class="btn btn-warning text-white font-weight-bold" asp-action="Create">Create New</a>
    </p>
}
<section class="ftco-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <div class="featured-carousel owl-carousel">
                    @foreach (var post in Model)
                    {
                    <div class="item">
                        <div class="work">
                            <div class="img d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center rounded">
                                <img class="img-fluid" style="width:100%" src=@_fileService.DecodeImage(post.ImageData, post.ContentType) alt="card image cap">
                            </div>
                            <div class="text pt-3 w-100 text-center">
                                <h3 class="font-weight-bold text-white">@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => post.Title)</h3>
                                <h3 class="font-weight-bold text-white"><em>Posted on @Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => post.Created)</em></h3>
                                <hr />
                            </div>
                            <div class="text pt-3 w-100 text-center">
                                <h3 class="text-white">@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => post.Abstract)</h3>
                            </div>
                            <a asp-action="Details" asp-controller="Posts" asp-route-slug="@post.Slug" class="btn btn-warning d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
                                <h6 class="text-white font-weight-bold">Read Full Post</h6> &rarr;
                            </a>
                        </div>
                        @if (User.IsInRole("Administrator"))
                        {
                            <div class="btn btn-warning d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
                                <a class="text-white font-weight-bold" asp-action="Edit" asp-route-id="@post.Id">Edit</a> |
                                <a class="text-white font-weight-bold" asp-action="Details" asp-route-slug="@post.Slug">Details</a> |
                                <a class="text-white font-weight-bold" asp-action="Delete" asp-route-id="@post.Id">Delete</a>
                            </div>
                        }
                    </div>
                    }
                    </div>
           </div>
    </div>
</div>
</section>